{"id":607056,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/【cdtv】台湾人限定的最强幻术：九二共室/","date":"2019-03-07T05:40:22Z","modified":"2019-03-07T05:40:22Z","title":"【CDTV】台湾人限定的最强幻术：九二共室","content":"<p>@台視新聞 TTV NEWS：曾奪下世界紙牌魔術冠軍的魔術師吳何，擅長用表演結合時事，最近以紙牌魔術暗諷「九二共識」，將黑桃九、紅心二互換，形容兩岸各執一詞，最後將紙牌撕成兩半，關進盒子，讓「九二共處一室」，給大家「各自表述」的空間，精闢的比喻，引來網友討論，輕鬆地談論嚴肅議題，也讓這支魔術影片，短短4天，就有超過75萬人次觀看。</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IjadUKGivGo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4j23Eth2aio?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%ae%e7%a4%be-%e9%87%8d%e5%9b%9e1992%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e4%bc%9a%e8%b0%88%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e7%9c%8b%e6%87%82%e4%b9%9d%e4%ba%8c%e5%85%b1%e8%af%86/\">中央社 | 重回1992香港会谈一次看懂九二共识</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/%e7%88%b1%e6%80%9d%e6%83%b3-%e6%9d%a8%e7%ab%8b%e5%ae%aa%ef%bc%9a%e4%b9%9d%e4%ba%8c%e5%85%b1%e8%af%86%e5%bb%bf%e5%91%a8%e5%b9%b4%e5%9b%9e%e9%a1%be%e4%b8%8e%e5%8f%8d%e6%80%9d/\">爱思想 | 杨立宪：九二共识廿周年回顾与反思</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/%e3%80%90cdtv%e3%80%91%e5%a4%a7%e9%99%86%e9%9d%92%e5%b9%b4%e8%af%b4%e4%b8%ba%e4%bb%80%e4%b9%88%e5%8f%b0%e6%b9%be%e4%b8%8d%e6%83%b3%e5%92%8c%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e7%bb%9f%e4%b8%80/\">【CDTV】大陆青年说为什么台湾不想和中国统一</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/%E3%80%90cdtv%E3%80%91%E9%A6%86%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80-%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A7%E5%85%9A%E7%BB%9F%E6%B2%BB%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6/\">【CDTV】陈之汉：拒绝统一 拒绝习近平 共产党统治现状</a></p></blockquote>\n","author"